============================================================
VERDICT
============================================================
If all ratios are within ±5% of 1.0, the two implementations
are numerically identical on this LC.  Any residual real-GRB
discrepancy must come from data preprocessing (detector mask,
energy band, background subtraction), not from the algorithm.
